      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with the scent of fresh leather and untouched upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine is whisper-quiet, the transmission is seamless, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. It has been meticulously garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook, making it a rare find for a discerning collector or a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
