    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The engine breathes through individual throttle bodies, pulling hard to an 8,400 RPM redline. It comes equipped with the Competition Package (ZCP), featuring a 10mm lowered suspension and remapped Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for superior lateral grip. Maintenance is up to date with documented rod bearing replacement and a recent throttle actuator service. The limited-slip M-differential remains tight, and the subframe shows no signs of fatigue. While the paint retains a deep gloss, minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its history as a driven machine.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
