    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both performance and sophistication. Meticulously maintained and showing pride of ownership, it offers a refined driving experience supported by a robust mechanical profile. The interior cabin remains composed and elegant, while the exterior retains a commanding presence. This offering represents a superior balance of luxury and long-term value, having undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure its continued reliability on the road.",
