      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The powertrain remains stock, delivering linear torque through the factory variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, ensuring precise turn-in and chassis composure. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are synchronized and track-ready. This is a robust, analog machine for the enthusiast who prioritizes visceral feedback and engineering integrity over showroom perfection.",
